posting_body: ['Pricing subject to change without notice, contact us today.', 'Welcome to Harrington Square', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 146', 'OR Text', '146', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to chat!', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1002 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Experience true balanced living through a combination of modern architecture and the serene views of the beautiful Pacific Northwest!', 'Located just outside of Seattle, and minutes away from I-405 and the Landing in Renton, Harrington Square is pet-friendly and offers studio, one, and two bedroom homes with large open floor plans flaunting exquisite finishes and detail including granite counter tops and stainless steel appliances.', "Find your sanctuary relaxing in your home, gathering with good friends, shopping nearby retail, and dining at the neighborhood's finest restaurants and cafes.", 'At Harrington Square rediscover luxury and service.', 'Features:', 'Walk-in Closets*, 9 Foot Ceilings, Pantry, Custom Cabinetry, Mountain and Lakeviews Available, Private Balcony or Patio, Stainless Steel Appliances, Hardwood Flooring, Granite Countertops, Open Layouts, Washer/Dryer in Home', 'Community Amenities:', 'Smoke-Free Community, Fitness on Demand, Pet Park, Wifi lounge, BBQ Area, Controlled Access, Package Lockers 24/7, Disability Access, On Bus Line & Near Renton Transit Center, EV Charging Stations, Additional Storage, Yoga Studio, Community Outdoor Deck, 24 Hour Fitness Center, Garage Parking, Short Term Leases Available', 'Pet Policy', 'Our homes accommodate two pets per home.', 'Additional deposits and breed restrictions may apply.', 'Please contact our leasing professionals for more details.', 'Income Requirements:', 'Combined income amount of Gross monthly income must be at least 2.5x the monthly rent', 'Visit This Website to See More:', '<URL>', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', '326h7eedwS']
